column3: A (contractual) term regarding privacy that expresses permissions, prohibitions, and obligations
A preference regarding privacy term(s) which indicates the terms are preferred over other terms, or are acceptable, or are unacceptable
A negotiation between parties regarding choosing the appropriate privacy terms
A request to initiate a privacy negotiation
An endpoint, such as a URL or an address, where privacy related communications can be made
A record of a privacy negotiation, including both accepted and rejected negotiations as well as the creation of contracts
